*** NEW AREA: The World of Dragonlance ***

A vast new region inspired by the world of Krynn has opened! Explore
the treetop village of Solace, the ruins of Xak Tsaroth, the fortress
of Pax Tharkas, and the dark Temple of Takhisis. Four new quests await
adventurers of all levels:

  1. The Blue Crystal Staff  - Begin in Solace, speak with Goldmoon
  2. The Disks of Mishakal   - Seek Riverwind in Xak Tsaroth
  3. Liberation of Pax Tharkas - Find Elistan in the fortress prison
  4. Defeat Takhisis         - Speak with Fizban at the dark temple

Quests are tiered by difficulty -- start with the Staff and work your
way up to face the Queen of Darkness herself!

To reach Solace, travel west from the plains.
